   Armbruster, W. Scott, Univ Portsmouth, Sch Biol Sci, Portsmouth PO1 2DY, Hants, England.
   Armbruster, W. Scott, Univ Alaska, Inst Arctic Biol, Fairbanks, AK 99775 USA.
   Armbruster, W. Scott, Norwegian Univ Sci \& Technol, Dept Biol, N-7491 Trondheim, Norway.
   Muchhala, Nathan, Univ Toronto, Dept Ecol \& Evolut, Toronto, ON M5S 3G5, Canada.},
